
File system API for
Q when/defer-style promises


THE API
-------

open(path, options)

read(path, options)

write(path, options)

append(path, options)

list(path)

listTree(path)

stat(path)

isFile(path)

isDirectory(path)

lastModified(path)

split(path)

join(paths)
join(...paths)

resolve(...paths)

normal(...paths)

absolute(path)

canonical(path)

contains(parent, child)

relative(source, target)

isAbsolute(path)

isRelative(path)

isRoot(path)

root(path)

directory(path)

base(path, extension)

extension(path)

ROOT

    `/` on Unix
    `\` on Windows

SEPARATOR

    `/` on Unix
    `\` on Windows

ALT_SEPARATOR

    undefined on Unix
    `/` on Windows


